data.description: This captivating townhouse, has a  3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence offers a spacious haven for modern living. The bright, open layout ushers you into a world of boundless possibilities, as natural light dances through the rooms. The kitchen, a true focal point of this home, showcases sleek stainless steel appliances and stunning quartz countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms - a dream for both culinary enthusiasts and those with an appreciation for modern elegance. Additionally, this townhouse feels like an independent house, providing an extra layer of privacy and autonomy. Backyard with a private pool and room for a garden. NO HOA AND NO RESTRICTIONS. IT'S A MUST SEE IN WELLINGTON. Seller gives $ 3,000.00 credit towards closing costs for the buyer.
